Entertainment in the analogical age... The Hellbrunn Castle is situated very close to Salzburg and since hundreds of years it offers a variety of refreshing water tricks and jokes to its visitors. You better leave your electronics at home, you are going to get wet! In the picture you see a statue and a laughing demon activated trough water flow.
